;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2394&quot; data-end=&quot;2401&quot;&gt;Result:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;overflow-visible! px-0!&quot; data-start=&quot;2403&quot; data-end=&quot;2454&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative w-full mt-4 mb-1&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;contents&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pe-11 pt-3&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative z-0 flex max-w-full&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; class=&quot;q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-scroller&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Medium Priority&lt;br&gt;Inspect within 2–7 days&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;2456&quot; data-end=&quot;2459&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;4a10vp&quot; data-start=&quot;2461&quot; data-end=&quot;2497&quot;&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="560" y="6357.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iIwD6QwnB8rfQwbx0LGv-19" edge="1" parent="1" source="iIwD6QwnB8rfQwbx0LGv-17" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="iIwD6QwnB8rfQwbx0LGv-18" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iIwD6QwnB8rfQwbx0LGv-17" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=18;" value="Customer message“My vehicle takes longer to start and battery voltage is 11.4 V” &#xa; ↓&#xa;LLM reads and understands text &#xa; ↓&#xa;Extracts important facts &#xa; ↓&#xa;Applies prompt rules / domain knowledge &#xa; ↓&#xa;Identifies missing information &#xa; ↓&#xa;Generates safe recommendation" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="320" width="560" x="290" y="7320" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iIwD6QwnB8rfQwbx0LGv-18" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;p&gt;Internally, the LLM is used mainly as a &lt;strong&gt;reasoning + language generation layer&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Customer message&lt;br/&gt;“My vehicle takes longer to start and battery voltage is 11.4 V”&lt;br/&gt;        ↓&lt;br/&gt;LLM reads and understands text&lt;br/&gt;        ↓&lt;br/&gt;Extracts important facts&lt;br/&gt;        ↓&lt;br/&gt;Applies prompt rules / domain knowledge&lt;br/&gt;        ↓&lt;br/&gt;Identifies missing information&lt;br/&gt;        ↓&lt;br/&gt;Generates safe recommendation&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Internally it works like this&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4&gt;1. Text understanding&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;The LLM identifies:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Symptom = longer starting time&lt;br/&gt;Battery voltage = 11.4 V&lt;br/&gt;Question = what should I do?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h4&gt;2. Context interpretation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;It understands that:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;11.4 V battery voltage + slow starting&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;may indicate a weak/low battery condition, but it does &lt;strong&gt;not confirm failure&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;3. Safety reasoning&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;The LLM checks missing information:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Was voltage measured engine ON or OFF?&lt;br/&gt;Was the car idle for some time?&lt;br/&gt;Temperature?&lt;br/&gt;Vehicle age?&lt;br/&gt;Warning lights?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Because these are missing, it avoids saying:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Battery is dead.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Instead it says:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Battery may be low. Please inspect.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h4&gt;4. Rule or ML output integration&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;In real system, LLM may receive structured output from ML/rule engine:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;{&lt;br/&gt;  &quot;symptom&quot;: &quot;slow_start&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;  &quot;battery_voltage&quot;: 11.4,&lt;br/&gt;  &quot;risk_level&quot;: &quot;Medium&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;  &quot;recommended_tests&quot;: [&lt;br/&gt;    &quot;battery health test&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;    &quot;load test&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;    &quot;alternator check&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;    &quot;starter motor inspection&quot;&lt;br/&gt;  ],&lt;br/&gt;  &quot;drive_advice&quot;: &quot;short trips only if vehicle starts normally&quot;&lt;br/&gt;}&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then LLM converts it into customer-friendly text.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;5. Final response generation&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;The LLM writes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Your battery voltage is relatively low and slow starting increases concern.&lt;br/&gt;Please schedule battery and charging-system inspection within 2–7 days.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Best architecture&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;User Complaint&lt;br/&gt;     ↓&lt;br/&gt;LLM extracts symptoms&lt;br/&gt;     ↓&lt;br/&gt;Rule/ML Risk Engine calculates risk&lt;br/&gt;     ↓&lt;br/&gt;LLM explains result in simple language&lt;br/&gt;     ↓&lt;br/&gt;Customer receives advisory&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Important point&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;LLM should &lt;strong&gt;not directly decide final mechanical diagnosis&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Better design:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;LLM = Understand + Explain&lt;br/&gt;ML/Rules = Score Risk&lt;br/&gt;Technician = Confirm Diagnosis&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1810" width="590" x="510" y="7850" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram id="-vfwb60VO9x_wGA4clrH" name="Page-12">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1239" dy="768" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="isdayxp9qJtYUWVr0dbm-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=19;" value="User Question &#xa; ↓&#xa;Convert to Embedding &#xa; ↓&#xa;Vector Database Search &#xa; ↓&#xa;Retrieve Relevant Documents &#xa; ↓&#xa;Build PromptSYSTEM+RETRIEVED CONTEXT+USER QUESTION &#xa; ↓&#xa;LLM &#xa; ↓&#xa;Grounded Answer" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="340" width="560" x="80" y="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="isdayxp9qJtYUWVr0dbm-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=19;" value="&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1ap3224&quot; data-start=&quot;246&quot; data-end=&quot;266&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot;&gt;Why OCR is needed&lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchor&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;k7jxte&quot; data-start=&quot;268&quot; data-end=&quot;303&quot;&gt;1. Scanned PDFs are just images&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;305&quot; data-end=&quot;333&quot;&gt;Suppose you scan an invoice.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;335&quot; data-end=&quot;347&quot;&gt;Without OCR:&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;pre class=&quot;overflow-visible! px-0!&quot; data-start=&quot;349&quot; data-end=&quot;464&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative w-full mt-4 mb-1&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;contents&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pe-11 pt-3&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative z-0 flex max-w-full&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; class=&quot;q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-scroller&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;PDF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt; ┌──────────────────────┐&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt; │  Image of Invoice    │&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt; │  (Pixels only)       │&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt; └──────────────────────┘&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;466&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;The computer only sees pixels, not words.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;509&quot; data-end=&quot;542&quot;&gt;For example, it cannot recognize:&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;544&quot; data-end=&quot;612&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1j5ikq2&quot; data-start=&quot;544&quot; data-end=&quot;571&quot;&gt;&#xa;Invoice Number: INV-10025&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s25o75&quot; data-start=&quot;572&quot; data-end=&quot;594&quot;&gt;&#xa;Customer: Volkswagen&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;e2hd9y&quot; data-start=&quot;595&quot; data-end=&quot;612&quot;&gt;&#xa;Amount: ₹85,000&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;614&quot; data-end=&quot;617&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1jtj3ni&quot; data-start=&quot;619&quot; data-end=&quot;647&quot;&gt;2. OCR extracts the text&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;649&quot; data-end=&quot;659&quot;&gt;After OCR:&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;pre class=&quot;overflow-visible! px-0!&quot; data-start=&quot;661&quot; data-end=&quot;834&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative w-full mt-4 mb-1&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;contents&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full min-h-0 min-w-0&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pe-11 pt-3&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative z-0 flex max-w-full&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; class=&quot;q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-scroller&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;    │&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ▼&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;OCR Engine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;    │&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ▼&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;Extracted Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;Invoice Number : INV-10025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;Customer       : Volkswagen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;Amount         : ₹85,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;Date           : 24-Jun-2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;836&quot; data-end=&quot;888&quot;&gt;Now the document becomes searchable and processable.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1040" width="500" x="150" y="880" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="isdayxp9qJtYUWVr0dbm-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=26;fontStyle=1" value="Once U will be back pls raise ur hands ." vertex="1">
